{"tid":1583631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖條杏加橙又想唔上身","createTime":"2019-09-20T16:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T17:07:31.000Z","uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"952cabfe43ef8c9c7a85b1f8d68ed1bf0ef5991d","tid":1583631,"uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"把口話唔撕連濃， 但叫人帶晒剷仔，清潔劑做野，食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【連儂牆】何君堯凌晨突稱不會「清牆」　但發指引指撕海報不違法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/377706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F377706&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=d5273238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/377706</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯今早（21日）發起「清潔香港行動」，本身稱清理18區連儂牆，不過何君堯凌晨12時發聲明，稱為了安全起見，他們不會清理連儂牆，只會清理街道垃圾；又揚言若遇上任何挑釁，他們會忍讓，「當安全受到威脅之時，各人會聽從相關團長指示，迴避或全面撤離，有需要時，打999向警方求助！」<br />\n<br />\n不過在何君堯向參與者發出「行動指引」，明確指出若撕走牆身的海報及紙張，不會被拘捕，因正行動相應的公民權利消除公眾地方垃圾，同時又建議參與者帶備九樣裝備，包括口罩、小鏟子、勞工手套、清潔膠漬的清潔劑、水和毛巾、垃圾袋、乾淨替換的衣物、眼罩和掃把。"},{"pid":"ea36838c69ce14133231426cd532751f108ad8d7","tid":1583631,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"79a68902406daab7d094086f9ef157896c15c970","tid":1583631,"uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5574732508b993b47b80e5886b3ba3c6fe54554e","tid":1583631,"uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce3b8e125e3c62fcd394c63953014b4604f6424","tid":1583631,"uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86592dc7e02a50c58a91dd8eb8c239aed7bd4830","tid":1583631,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"哈哈，又笠水"}]}